snippet.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban PS2 Walkthrough - Part 03
snippet.description:
==Neville and the Ghoul==
Harry and Ron free Neville from a Ghoul on the 5th Floor, but they return to the Common Room to find that Sirius Black has attacked!
